==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Charless Wain
<hw>Charles's Wain</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <ety>[<ets>Charles</ets> +
<ets>wain</ets>; cf. AS. <ets>Carles w⟦aemac⟧n</ets> (for
<ets>w⟦ae⟧gn</ets>), Sw. <ets>karlvagnen</ets>, Dan.
<ets>karlsvogn</ets>. See <er>Churl</er>, and <er>Wain</er>.]</ety>
<fld>(Astron.)</fld> <def>The group of seven stars, commonly called the
<xex>Big Dipper</xex>, in the constellation <xex>Ursa Major</xex>, or
<xex>Great Bear</xex>. See <er>Ursa major</er>, under
<er>Ursa</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

<p><note>⟦hand⟧ The name is sometimes also applied to the
Constellation.</note>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Charlie</ent>⟦br⟧
